title: Death By A Thousand Cuts
description:
Taylor inspired a movie that inspired Taylor to write a song! That's next level Taylor inspiring Taylor!
What is the movie that inspired Taylor to write this song? And how did this song help Taylor validate herself? We break it all down!
What did we miss? What should we discuss next? There are lots of ways to get ahold of us!
